Matthew 21-45 <pb/>When the chief priests and the Pharisees heard his parables, they perceived that he was speaking about them.
Matthew 21-46 And <f>ⓨ</f>although they were seeking to arrest him, <f>ⓩ</f>they feared the crowds, because they held him to be <f>ⓐ</f>a prophet.
